Your photo albums, trophies, and refrigerator art represent the best of the best - the rest is in deep storage or no longer in your life. People can be a little mysterious sometimes, but you'll gladly try to figure them out. If they're related to you, you definitely have their number, even if you'd rather not call it. Friendship is so much easier than the complications of family.

answersResultList.title: True Cancer.
answersResultList.resultContent: Your world revolves around your family and friends. If they need you for anything, you're there. Your home is somewhere between a womb and a shrine, depending on whether you're taking care of others or preserving the things they've left in your keeping. You know your way around business and personal relationships, and you excel at pushing the right buttons. Is that guidance or manipulation? You're a caring member of the community and a conservative investor, because the future is in some ways more important than the present. Legacy issues concern you deeply. You want to be remembered with love.

answersResultList.title: Mostly Cancer.
answersResultList.resultContent: You want to make a difference in the world, but unlike a true Cancer, you'll spend a lot of time out in the field instead of working from a home base. Affectionate as you are, you can be selective with how much energy you put into professional and personal relationships. You have intuitive abilities but don't always let them guide you. Sometimes this gets you in trouble, but other times you're OK playing it by the book. Another difference between you and a true Cancer is that your private life is no big secret. Well, some of the time, anyway.
